Create a list of different room types to randomly pick from including a treasure room and an escape area
Create a list of different enemies to randomly pick from
Create a list of different treasures to randomly pick from
Randomly pick room type
  If treasure room
    randomly pick treasure 
  Elif escape area
    Start a battle with the final boss a dragon
    If player wins
      The game ends and player escapes
    Else
      Game over and restart
  Else
    Randomly pick an enemy from the list
    Start a battle with the enemy
    If player wins
      Continue exploring the room
        If player says continue
          Randomly pick another room
        Elif player says investigate
          Depending on the room they might find clues to help them moving forward
    Else
      Game over
  
